E2BR3AU.original: ~z~He's a bit like you and Big Tone actually.
~z~Don't bring down the positive energy, Lopez. Me and my brother are having fun today.
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~别坏我们的兴致啊，Lopez。我和我弟弟是出来嗨的。

E2BR3AU.original: ~z~Hey, I got a gift for you bitches. Some headsets. So I can tell you what to do later.
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~喂，我给你俩准备了礼物。一对耳机。这样待会儿我就能指点你们了。

E2BR3AU.original: ~z~Come on, little B. Hey, what do you take me for?
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~得了吧，小B崽子。你把我当什么人了？

E2BR3AU.original: ~z~Well, I meant the part about you having no cock, you fucking loser. Toughen up!
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~行吧，阳痿那句是真的，你个废物。坚强点啊！

E2BR3AU.original: ~z~It's good to have Lopez along too, right? Hey, the three amigos.
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~有Lopez一起也很好啊，对吧？嘿，三个大兄弟。

E2BR3AU.original: ~z~Dude, you're putting me off. Come on.
~z~Okay, we got a straight here. Open 'em up.
~z~Yeah, well maybe you should keep to pruning roses and stay out this game then. I'm out bro.
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~好，你还是老老实实修剪玫瑰吧，别违法乱纪了。我走了，兄弟。

E2BR3AU.original: ~z~I'm gonna get arrested, I know it.
~z~ Fuck it. Beta. Gamma. You're the Omega man. Bottom of the food chain. You're a bitch's bitch.
E2BR3AU.translated: ~z~算了。二流、三流，你压根就不入流。食物链的最底层，贱逼中的贱逼。
